{"id": "269b5eafa76beb2d1c9408ed96b6bb1c46b9428503fc29737e4b76966dc02728", "item_id": "ecd99ee5e4:0", "text": "Baking out textures involves two easy steps."}
{"id": "26307e5f5a747f523aa5a4c22f20bee219450c8d403ea89d85a9ecb5d59155ef", "item_id": "ecd99ee5e4:2", "text": "Baking"}
{"id": "0895e3ea3d207f413c6e9c0870ef6824c14f2142a3f719d7dabf315b55a20792", "item_id": "ecd99ee5e4:3", "text": "for more information."}
{"id": "91e09092ceca56c017201db5f726cee4be295136ec2645f65de86388ea54909a", "item_id": "ecd99ee5e4:4", "text": "The user should supply UVs (UV mapped) for the object to be baked."}
{"id": "3c0c801ab395f8dd9e34ed3df257f6b4cb938ef45150adba96c5d696780a2462", "item_id": "ecd99ee5e4:5", "text": "Set Bake Hider"}
{"id": "8eb0f606aa71ed3f8b63d141789aa3a35f78c874a278600b281c3e7d89df4971", "item_id": "ecd99ee5e4:6", "text": "Instead of using raytrace, set it to"}
{"id": "3c8c082e47323c2858b0898b39c045b39b6f5874133f77d89f9fe9c8034b2e1d", "item_id": "ecd99ee5e4:7", "text": "bake"}
{"id": "bb2c7f454230c760ffa3d0585c74c20337f158e1512b4e22587937cbe00f5b71", "item_id": "ecd99ee5e4:9", "text": "Add PxrBakeTexture"}
{"id": "b9c842f2eb4eb2bdb1692a27b68838d3e346698b4d1b08a171914e52b0d878cc", "item_id": "ecd99ee5e4:10", "text": "In your RIS Network, add a"}
{"id": "b4ceaff3b9cf94e655994dafdf1ef23d69440d3a514a31b9d3be8aca65bdbb17", "item_id": "ecd99ee5e4:14", "text": "PxrBakeTexture"}
{"id": "b2cea521e1544a2b13717fb1e28010e7bc2e4d188b88886900481db7c93db078", "item_id": "ecd99ee5e4:12", "text": "VOP.  Wire its output to a PxrSurface color parameter so it will get evaluated."}
{"id": "0bc6121ecf69e8e47d31096795839fb434cee88fc597dd0dd6efcb8b291c2ee3", "item_id": "ecd99ee5e4:13", "text": "In the PxrBakeTexture VOP, set its output FileName.  See"}
{"id": "ce27e3f6bc4e8012f89de270653d13020fb3f1e5a115bbf1029ef317d01712d9", "item_id": "ecd99ee5e4:15", "text": "for descriptions of each parameter."}
